Interface SettingsKey

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SettingsFloatKey, SettingsGroupKey, SettingsIntegerKey, SettingsStringKey

    public interface SettingsKey
    Interface SettingsKey define a contract about the usability of keys, regardless of their type.
    See Also:
    SettingsFloatKey, SettingsStringKey, SettingsGroupKey, SettingsIntegerKey
